import React from 'react'
import { NavLink } from 'react-router-dom'
import { AppBar, Toolbar, Typography, Paper, Tabs } from '@material-ui/core'
import Tab from '@material-ui/core/tabs'

const NavBar = () => {
    return (
        <AppBar>
            <Toolbar>
                <Typography variant="h5" color="inherit">
                    The Calorie Police
                </Typography>
                <Paper>
                    <Tabs value={2} indicatorColor="primary" textColor="primary" centered>
  
                    </Tabs>
                </Paper>
             
            </Toolbar>
        </AppBar>
    )
}

export default NavBar
